description: In search of an authentic Chicago-style dog, as well as training and employment for individuals with disabilities in the food service industry, Debby Graham, the executive director of Centerforce, a local nonprofit devoted to providing such opportunities, created Hometown Dogs. Now the streets of the greater Lakewood area and Puget Sound are being treated to delicious gourmet Vienna Beef Signature hot dogs, thanks to this super cool crew. You’re sure to savor this craveable selection of classic national creations, like the Chicago Dog (with mustard, onions, neon green relish, sport peppers, tomatoes, celery salt, pickle spear, on a poppy seed bun), New York Dog (with hot sauerkraut and spicy brown mustard), and Seattle Dog too (with cream cheese, onions, tomatoes, jalapeños, and sauerkraut), and these are only a few!If you’re hungry for food of fantastic quality and for wonderful attributes in your community, Hometown Dogs is the certainly the truck for you. .
name: Hometown Dogs
